{
  "message": "test(ansi): accept insta snapshots - migrate .snap.new to canonical .snap files\n\nRun cargo insta accept to promote all 11 pending ANSI test snapshots\nfrom .snap.new (pending review) to .snap (accepted baseline). The\n.snap.new files are deleted and replaced with the canonical .snap files\nthat insta uses for future regression detection.\n\nAccepted snapshots:\n- bg_colors_16, bg_colors_256, bg_colors_truecolor\n- fg_colors_16, fg_colors_256, fg_colors_truecolor, fg_colors_nocolor\n- text_attributes\n- cursor_move, cursor_position\n- hyperlinks\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
